race.comment: BAREFOOT ZULU (4) is progressing well scoring last time out (29.52) at this track and bringing up his 10th career win. Has a good record at this journey. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Can make it two on the bounce. KING OWEN (1) comes off an average effort last start when fifth at Sandown over 515m behind Urana Xavier (29.97) in a Grade 4/5. Was a winner prior to that. Key player if finds best. SWEET SUNDOWN (7) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with four wins and a placing from seven tries. In the money last time at Sandown (29.56) in a Grade 5, finishing a 6 length second. Looks a key chance on best figures. UTRILLO BALE (2) can find the frame without surprising.
